a young man's fancy turns to obsession.

53
00:04:10,035 --> 00:04:12,400
Hello there.

54
00:04:12,435 --> 00:04:13,400
Oh my heavenly days.

55
00:04:13,435 --> 00:04:15,700
Rex, look! It's George.

56
00:04:15,735 --> 00:04:17,800
