he doesn't want you to go out with me.

72
00:05:06,335 --> 00:05:09,100
Rex, are you jealous?

73
00:05:09,135 --> 00:05:10,000
No.

74
00:05:10,035 --> 00:05:14,100
It's true that we dated during the separation,
but George and I are just friends now, aren't we?

75
00:05:14,135 --> 00:05:16,100
It's certainly platonic.

76
00:05:16,135 --> 00:05:17,100
But if you feel threatened--

77
00:05:17,135 --> 00:05:22,200
I don't feel threatened.

78
00:05:22,235 --> 00:05:26,500
Good! Then it's a date.

79
00:05:26,535 --> 00:05:28,300
So are you going to make a purchase today?

80
00:05:28,335 --> 00:05:32,000
You know, I have finally convinced Rex
to buy his first orchid.

81
00:05:32,035 --> 00:05:33,100
Make sure you study up.

82
00:05:33,135 --> 00:05:37,000
