you can get rid of almost anything.

86
00:05:46,435 --> 00:05:49,237
See you Friday.
- Bye.

87
00:05:53,935 --> 00:05:58,400
Mrs Solís! What a surprise.
We haven't seen you here in quite some time.

88
00:05:58,435 --> 00:06:03,200
