a downsizing phase. But we stepped out of it.

89
00:06:03,235 --> 00:06:05,700
Life is good.

90
00:06:05,735 --> 00:06:07,800
Oh, and this would make it so much better.

91
00:06:07,835 --> 00:06:11,794
Excellent.
Slip inside, see how that feels.

92
00:06:14,735 --> 00:06:17,900
I'd love to have this in my driveway by Saturday.

93
00:06:17,935 --> 00:06:20,900
