I want everyone to see it.

94
00:06:20,935 --> 00:06:23,100
Exciting. What's the occasion?

95
00:06:23,135 --> 00:06:24,800
I'm throwing my husband a going-away party.

96
00:06:24,835 --> 00:06:26,900
Really? Where's he going?

97
00:06:26,935 --> 00:06:31,100
It's, um -- a sort of
government-sponsored sabbatical.

98
00:06:31,135 --> 00:06:34,700
How long will he be gone?
- Eight months.

99
00:06:34,735 --> 00:06:37,235
Six, with good behavior.

100
00:06:38,835 --> 00:06:41,200
Isn't the leather interior wonderful?

101
00:06:41,235 --> 00:06:44,900
It is.
It just smells a little intense.

102
00:06:44,935 --> 00:06:50,803
Because it was imported from Italy.
It's 100% Italian calf.

103
00:06:56,935 --> 00:07:00,800
I'm so sorry.
It hit me out of nowhere.

104
00:07:00,835 --> 00:07:05,100
It was so weird.
Smells are making me nauseous lately.

105
00:07:05,135 --> 00:07:08,000
Boobs tender? Achey back?

106
00:07:08,035 --> 00:07:10,200
Yeah! Has it been going around?

107
00:07:10,235 --> 00:07:12,200
Only for centuries.

108
00:07:12,235 --> 00:07:14,700
I went through it all
when I was carrying my oldest.

109
00:07:14,735 --> 00:07:19,600
The truth is, you'll never fit a child seat
in the back of that tiny Spider anyway.

110
00:07:19,635 --> 00:07:21,900
The 4-doors are much roomier.

111
