176
00:11:37,435 --> 00:11:40,600
I heard you and Edie broke into Paul Young's house.

177
00:11:40,635 --> 00:11:42,300
Who told you that?

178
00:11:42,335 --> 00:11:44,500
Edie.

179
00:11:44,535 --> 00:11:48,500
Well-- yeah, we did.

180
00:11:48,535 --> 00:11:50,900
