would just give him false hope.

208
00:13:13,235 --> 00:13:17,500
I certainly don't want to hurt him-- again.

209
00:13:17,535 --> 00:13:19,800
No. You don't.

210
00:13:19,835 --> 00:13:23,600
I think it would be a good idea
to switch pharmacies.

211
00:13:23,635 --> 00:13:25,007
Really?

212
00:13:27,935 --> 00:13:33,700
OK.
You know what I'll miss most about him?

213
00:13:33,735 --> 00:13:37,000
George always has a way of
making me feel good about myself.

214
00:13:37,035 --> 00:13:40,584
Yeah, he's a terrific guy.

215
00:13:41,535 --> 00:13:46,500
Honey, do your hands still tremble
when they touch me?

216
00:13:46,535 --> 00:13:51,200
