223
00:14:15,035 --> 00:14:19,000
Oh, it's right over there, Mrs Solís.
Help yourself.

224
00:14:19,035 --> 00:14:20,213
Thank you.

225
00:14:23,435 --> 00:14:26,100
What did I tell you about being rude to customers?

226
00:14:26,135 --> 00:14:27,200
You'll stick a smile on your face,

227
00:14:27,235 --> 00:14:31,530
