with no one else to look at you!

228
00:14:33,435 --> 00:14:36,600
Bree! What a pleasant surprise!
What brings you here?

229
00:14:36,635 --> 00:14:39,900
Didn't we just fill Dr Van de Kamp's prescription last week?

230
00:14:39,935 --> 00:14:41,000
George, as it turns out,

231
00:14:41,035 --> 00:14:43,900
I won't be able to go with you to the bonsai expo.

232
00:14:43,935 --> 00:14:45,000
Oh, why not?

233
00:14:45,035 --> 00:14:48,500
I think it'd be a mistake for us
to spend too much time together.

234
00:14:48,535 --> 00:14:52,100
